{"questions":[{"category":"Company / Industry","question":"What major evolutions do you see coming for the Senior sales manager position?","suggested_answer":"Cite 1 or 2 trends (AI, CSR, new standards) to show you stay updated.","score":80},{"category":"Self-Awareness","question":"What are your three main weaknesses?","suggested_answer":"- Authoritarian: I am aware of this and I compensate by ....\n- Disorganized: I am aware of this and I compensate by ....\n- Competitive: I am aware of this and I compensate by ....","score":70},{"category":"Self-Awareness","question":"What are your top 3 strengths?","suggested_answer":"Leverage your declared strengths: Honest, Ambitious, Versatile. Illustrate them with concrete examples.","score":68},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you handle stress?","suggested_answer":"Give a concrete example where you stayed calm and prioritized tasks.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Tell me about a success you are proud of.","suggested_answer":"Use the STAR method (Situation, Task, Action, Result).","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Tell me about a failure and what you learned.","suggested_answer":"Be honest, take responsibility, and emphasize the lesson learned.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Where do you see yourself in 5 years?","suggested_answer":"Show ambition but stay consistent with the target role.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Why do you want to leave your current job?","suggested_answer":"Focus on what you are seeking (new challenges) rather than what you are fleeing.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Why should we hire you?","suggested_answer":"Summarize your 3 key skills that match the job description perfectly.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Do you prefer working alone or in a team?","suggested_answer":"Ideally show you are autonomous but appreciate collective dynamics.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What are your salary expectations?","suggested_answer":"Give a market-based range, don't give a fixed number too early.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What motivates you daily?","suggested_answer":"Talk about problem-solving, learning, or concrete impact.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you handle conflict with a colleague?","suggested_answer":"Prioritize direct and factual communication, without excessive emotion.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What is your ideal work environment?","suggested_answer":"Describe an environment that resembles the target company's.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Do you have any questions for us?","suggested_answer":"Always prepare 2-3 questions about the team, projects, or company vision.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Tell me about a time you had to learn something quickly.","suggested_answer":"Highlight your agility and adaptability.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you organize your workday?","suggested_answer":"Talk about tools (To-do list, calendar) and prioritization.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What attracted you to our company?","suggested_answer":"Show you researched their values or products.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Are you willing to travel for work?","suggested_answer":"Answer honestly based on your constraints.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you handle criticism?","suggested_answer":"Show you are open to constructive feedback to improve.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What was your most difficult project?","suggested_answer":"Describe the obstacles and how you overcame them.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What would your former boss say about you?","suggested_answer":"Cite factual positives (reliable, proactive).","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Which software do you master?","suggested_answer":"List those relevant to the job.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Do you like responsibilities?","suggested_answer":"Yes, if you aim for growth, but show you can also execute.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you deal with failure?","suggested_answer":"I analyze it to avoid repeating the mistake.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What are your hobbies?","suggested_answer":"Cite those that show an interesting facet of your personality.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Are you punctual?","suggested_answer":"Punctuality is a sign of respect.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you motivate others?","suggested_answer":"By example and positive encouragement.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Can you say no?","suggested_answer":"Yes, when it jeopardizes work quality or deadlines.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What management style do you prefer?","suggested_answer":"Management based on trust and autonomy.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What sets you apart from other candidates?","suggested_answer":"Your unique combination of experience X and skill Y.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Are you available immediately?","suggested_answer":"Give your exact notice period.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"Do you have other leads?","suggested_answer":"Yes, I am in an active process (shows you are in demand).","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What is your biggest professional fear?","suggested_answer":"Stagnation or boredom (shows your drive).","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"How do you handle a dissatisfied client?","suggested_answer":"Active listening, empathy, and solution proposal.","score":60},{"category":"Classic / HR","question":"What is a good leader to you?","suggested_answer":"Someone who inspires and grows their team.","score":60}]}